      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm working on a blog post arguing that any kind of government regulation of the internet—even stuff like anti-monopoly laws or content moderation rules—is fundamentally a violation of free speech and a step toward censorship. Can you help me find the strongest philosophical arguments to support this position?",
