      "content": "That's a good start. I want to make sure the post doesn't sound like it's just ignoring obvious counter-arguments. For example, when people bring up that regulation is necessary to stop hate speech or misinformation, how can I use these libertarian frameworks to argue that even those \"common sense\" protections are actually dangerous to free speech?",
